sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev
    participant CI
    participant Ext as External Action
    participant Reg as Registry
    participant Deploy

    Dev->>CI: Trigger pipeline
    CI->>Ext: Pull mutable action tag
    Ext-->>CI: Compromised behavior
    CI->>Reg: Publish artifact
    Deploy->>Reg: Pull artifact
    Deploy-->>Deploy: Reject if provenance gate enforced